---
title: Quick-Marinated Steak with Balsamic-Glazed Summer Vegetables
description: Rosemary, orange, garlic, and balsamic team up for a winning marinade in this weeknight steak dinner. Used on both the steak and glazed vegetables, it infuses the dish with the perfect balance of sweet, savory, and tangy flavor. The key to these veggies is caramelization—don’t take them out of the oven until they’re nice and golden brown!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/55661aa7f8b25e301e8b456a.jpg
